Master said
he didn't need to change his name.

00:32:09.319 --> 00:32:10.319
So?

00:32:11.039 --> 00:32:11.856
Mofeng's accepted.

00:32:11.880 --> 00:32:12.696
Accepted?

00:32:12.720 --> 00:32:13.720
Accepted.

00:32:14.200 --> 00:32:15.279
Should we keep kneeling?

00:32:15.519 --> 00:32:16.839
Rise. It's settled.

00:32:17.640 --> 00:32:18.640
I'm a senior now!

00:32:18.880 --> 00:32:20.176
- I have a junior now!
- Me too!

00:32:20.200 --> 00:32:21.216
- Mofeng.
- Mofeng.

00:32:21.400 --> 00:32:22.464
Mofeng.

00:32:23.519 --> 00:32:24.696
You're Master's disciple now.

00:32:24.720 --> 00:32:26.024
You're now my junior.

00:32:26.048 --> 00:32:26.976
Really?

00:32:27.000 --> 00:32:28.000
- I have a junior!
- Yes.

00:32:28.039 --> 00:32:29.176
I'm now his disciple?

00:32:29.200 --> 00:32:30.200
I have a junior brother!

00:32:30.359 --> 00:32:31.216
He.

00:32:31.240 --> 00:32:32.240
Accepted me!

00:32:32.279 --> 00:32:33.279
I have a master now!

00:32:51.480 --> 00:32:52.576
Chaofeng.

00:32:54.200 --> 00:32:55.200
Thank you.

00:32:55.599 --> 00:32:56.417
The Tinder Flower

00:32:56.441 --> 00:32:57.880
has greatly improved my condition.

00:32:59.039 --> 00:33:00.039
Tell me

00:33:00.319 --> 00:33:01.359
what you experienced

00:33:01.400 --> 00:33:02.519
on Liubo Island.

00:33:04.039 --> 00:33:05.039
Nothing, Madam.

00:33:12.720 --> 00:33:14.119
I never imagined

00:33:16.279 --> 00:33:17.279
that I could

00:33:18.680 --> 00:33:19.799
quietly

00:33:20.119 --> 00:33:21.160
take a hot bath

00:33:21.880 --> 00:33:23.519
like this.

00:33:28.079 --> 00:33:29.160
Meeting you all

00:33:29.440 --> 00:33:31.200
must be a blessing from my past life.

00:33:32.240 --> 00:33:33.960
To repay your kindness,

00:33:34.400 --> 00:33:35.599
even partially,

00:33:37.279 --> 00:33:38.319
I, Mei Ruohua,

00:33:38.640 --> 00:33:41.000
will do my best.

00:33:42.599 --> 00:33:43.599
Mei Chaofeng.

00:33:44.920 --> 00:33:45.920
Mei Chaofeng.

00:33:49.359 --> 00:33:50.359
Chaofeng.

00:33:52.640 --> 00:33:53.799
Let the past

00:33:54.680 --> 00:33:55.839
remain in the past.

00:33:57.279 --> 00:33:58.440
All previous suffering

00:33:59.000 --> 00:34:00.200
has gone.

