(It makes your life much more fun.)

00:35:10.559 --> 00:35:11.559
Come on. Cheers.

00:35:11.599 --> 00:35:12.416
- Come on.
- Come on.

00:35:12.440 --> 00:35:13.288
Bottoms up!

00:35:13.312 --> 00:35:14.312
Chaofeng is here.

00:35:14.848 --> 00:35:16.192
- Chaofeng.
- Come quick!

00:35:16.400 --> 00:35:17.615
Come on. Have a seat!

00:35:17.639 --> 00:35:18.752
Come on.

00:35:20.000 --> 00:35:21.000
Chaofeng.

00:35:21.119 --> 00:35:22.599
You should smile more often.

00:35:22.679 --> 00:35:23.679
It makes you look lovely.

00:35:24.679 --> 00:35:26.135
Xuanfeng, that's my seat.

00:35:26.159 --> 00:35:27.199
- Sit.
- Chaofeng.

00:35:28.000 --> 00:35:29.695
We owe our success to you.

00:35:29.719 --> 00:35:30.856
Without you,

00:35:30.880 --> 00:35:31.896
we might've been dead.

