Exactly! Come on!

00:35:41.920 --> 00:35:43.400
To celebrate our adventure

00:35:43.519 --> 00:35:44.400
and narrow escape!

00:35:44.480 --> 00:35:45.559
And Master's wife finally

00:35:45.599 --> 00:35:46.639
got the Tinder Flower.

