without you guys.

00:36:19.199 --> 00:36:20.199
Of course,

00:36:20.519 --> 00:36:21.519
Mofeng helped too.

00:36:21.639 --> 00:36:22.639
It's my pleasure.

00:36:23.480 --> 00:36:24.480
Speaking of which,

00:36:24.519 --> 00:36:25.736
raise your cup too, Mofeng.

00:36:25.760 --> 00:36:26.776
Right!

00:36:26.800 --> 00:36:27.800
Chen Xuanfeng.

00:36:28.360 --> 00:36:29.575
What's wrong with men drinking?

00:36:29.599 --> 00:36:30.880
- Cheers!
- Alright, cheers!

00:36:30.920 --> 00:36:31.920
Chen Xuanfeng.

00:36:33.199 --> 00:36:34.199
He has water.

00:36:34.760 --> 00:36:36.599
- That's not important.
- Let's drink!

00:36:36.880 --> 00:36:38.440
You guys,

00:36:38.519 --> 00:36:39.760
I'm so glad to meet you all.

00:36:40.119 --> 00:36:41.760
Drink at your pace. I'm finishing mine.

00:36:42.239 --> 00:36:43.239
At our pace?

00:36:43.800 --> 00:36:44.800
Yaoshi,

00:36:45.679 --> 00:36:47.760
look how happy they have been

00:36:48.239 --> 00:36:50.000
since Chaofeng came to the island.

00:36:50.360 --> 00:36:52.239
Lingfeng never drinks casually.

00:36:52.559 --> 00:36:53.575
Normally, he drinks

00:36:53.599 --> 00:36:55.976
- out of jars!
- Exactly!

00:36:56.000 --> 00:36:57.000
- Xuanfeng.
- Good.

00:36:57.024 --> 00:36:58.215
You drink with Lingfeng.

00:36:58.239 --> 00:36:59.175
Let's drink out of jars.

00:36:59.199 --> 00:37:00.096
We won't drink.

00:37:00.120 --> 00:37:01.416
How about you two drink together?

00:37:01.440 --> 00:37:02.257
Let's drink!

00:37:02.281 --> 00:37:03.639
I just want you to be happy.

00:37:05.400 --> 00:37:06.432
That's all I want.

00:37:08.032 --> 00:37:09.088
Exactly!

00:37:09.892 --> 00:37:10.788
- Come on.
- Cheers!

00:37:10.852 --> 00:37:12.044
Drink up!

00:37:12.068 --> 00:37:13.544
Let's drink!

00:37:13.568 --> 00:37:15.175
Lingfeng, I'll drink with you.

00:37:15.199 --> 00:37:16.760
I truly love days like this.

00:37:17.156 --> 00:37:18.336
Come on, drink!

00:37:18.719 --> 00:37:20.280
Don't blame the kids too much.

00:37:21.519 --> 00:37:22.416
Mofeng, come on.

00:37:22.440 --> 00:37:23.337
Raise your cup! Drink!

00:37:23.361 --> 00:37:24.495
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:37:24.519 --> 00:37:26.015
- Let's drink!
- Cheers!

00:37:26.039 --> 00:37:27.039
I don't blame them.

00:37:28.920 --> 00:37:30.320
They did it all for you.

00:37:39.639 --> 00:37:40.616
Mofeng.

00:37:40.640 --> 00:37:42.000
Taohua Island is your home.

00:37:42.624 --> 00:37:43.615
If anything happens,

00:37:43.639 --> 00:37:44.719
